41:27.580 --> 41:30.879
The slumped shoulders,
the pallor,

41:30.920 --> 41:33.912
like a turtle trying to
retreat back into its shell.

41:34.990 --> 41:37.151
I'm happy for you.

41:38.560 --> 41:41.950
